---
---
<header id="top" class="hero">
  <div class="wrap head-block">
    <div class="badge">✳ Drummer — Zurich</div>
    <h1>David<br />Krähen—<br />bühl<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
    <p class="bio">
      David Krähenbühl is a drummer from Zurich, working as an in-demand
      sideman and as co-bandleader of the instrumental trio loophole. His
      playing is groovy and atmospheric, shaped by musicians such as
      BADBADNOTGOOD, Yussef Dayes, and Tom Misch.
    </p>
    <div class="wobble-star" aria-hidden="true">✳</div>
  </div>
  <div class="wrap media-block">
    <div class="media-inner">
      <div class="frame">
        <img src="/images/dscf0580.jpg" alt="David Krähenbühl" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 64px 32px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .head-block { position: relative; }
  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--turquoise);
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--ink);
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 128px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .dot { color: var(--violet); }
  .bio {
    max-width: 520px;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 36px 0 0;
  }
  .wobble-star {
    position: absolute;
    top: -8px;
    right: 0;
    font-size: 72px;
    color: var(--pink);
    animation: wobble 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .media-block {
    margin-top: 56px;
  }
  .media-inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .frame {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 0 var(--violet);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--card-bg);
  }
  .frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
